text: Front-facing close-up shot of 74 high-quality vinyl PVC floral stickers featuring various floral designs; waterproof, scratch-proof, and sun-proof properties highlighted; stickers arranged neatly on a clean white background; no text or branding elements in the image; product centered with vibrant colors and glossy finish.
